@startuml
!theme plain

title UIM Application Autoscaler (AAS) - Component Architecture

actor "Platform Operator" as Operator
actor "Metrics Producer\n(CF/K8s App + Custom Exporter)" as Metrics

node "Kubernetes Cluster" {
  component "uim-sap-aas-service\n(vibe.d HTTP API)" as API
  database "In-Memory Store\n(AASStore)" as Store
  component "Policy Engine\n(AASService.evaluate)" as Engine
  component "CF Scale Adapter\n(triggerCFScale endpoint)" as CFAdapter
  component "K8s Deployment + Service + HPA" as K8sInfra
}

cloud "Cloud Foundry API" as CF

Operator --> API : Manage apps/policies
Metrics --> API : Push metric snapshots
API --> Engine : Evaluate policies
Engine --> Store : Read apps/policies
Engine --> Store : Write desired instances
API --> CFAdapter : Manual CF scale request
CFAdapter --> CF : Scale operation (adapter placeholder)
K8sInfra ..> API : Hosts service runtime

note right of Engine
Supports standard metrics:
- cpu
- memory
- response_time
- throughput
and custom metrics.
Computes scale_out / scale_in / hold.
end note

note bottom of Store
Data scope:
- AASApp
- AASScalingPolicy[]
- current_instances
end note

@enduml
